title: Vengeance Trance Sensation Vol. 1
description:
Vengeance Trance Sensation Vol. 1


20 newly composed and recorded trance hymns
drums, melodies, pads, fx, basslines etc... all with notes and BPM declaration
song kits contain verses (build ups), chorus and breaks
dry (without effects) and wet (effected) versions
all MIDIs of all melody-based tracks included
bonus sounds folder
fast and easy to implement in your production - looped, precisely cut at the beginning
over 1600 MB material spread over 750 files (Construction Kits consist of loops)
